ttp_template:
<group name="configuration_failover_mode_interface_last_failover_reason">
High Availability Configuration: {{CONFIGURATION | ORPHRASE}}
Failover Mode: {{FAILOVER_MODE | ORPHRASE}}
Last Failover Reason: {{LAST_FAILOVER_REASON | ORPHRASE}}
Last Failover Time: {{LAST_FAILOVER_TIME | ORPHRASE}}
PO1  {{STATE | ORPHRASE}}
{{INTERFACE | ORPHRASE}}  Up
</group>
cli_content:
High Availability Module (Active)
================================================
Primary Control Processor : Active
Secondary Control Processor: Standby
High Availability Configuration: Enabled
Failover Mode: Stateful
Last Failover Reason: Admin initiated
Last Failover Time: 2023-10-01 12:54:23

High Availability Interfaces:
Interface       State
----------------------
PO1             Up
PO2             Up
textfsm_template:
Value PRIMARY_CONTROL (\S+\s\S+)
Value SECONDARY_CONTROL (\S+\s\S+)
Value CONFIGURATION (\S+)
Value FAILOVER_MODE (\S+)
Value LAST_FAILOVER_REASON (.+)
Value LAST_FAILOVER_TIME (\S+\s+\S+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value STATE (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Primary Control Processor\s*:\s*${PRIMARY_CONTROL}\s*$$
  ^\s*Secondary Control Processor\s*:\s*${SECONDARY_CONTROL}\s*$$
  ^\s*High Availability Configuration\s*:\s*${CONFIGURATION}\s*$$
  ^\s*Failover Mode\s*:\s*${FAILOVER_MODE}\s*$$
  ^\s*Last Failover Reason\s*:\s*${LAST_FAILOVER_REASON}\s*$$
  ^\s*Last Failover Time\s*:\s*${LAST_FAILOVER_TIME}\s*$$
  ^\s*High Availability Interfaces:\s*$$
  ^\s*Interface\s+State\s*$$
  ^\s*${INTERFACE}\s+${STATE}\s*$$ -> Record
